## Test File Naming

```
[features-folder]/[feature]/
├── components/
│   ├── [Component].[ext]
│   └── [Component].test.[ext]    # Component test
├── hooks/
│   ├── [hook].[ext]
│   └── [hook].test.[ext]         # Hook test
└── __tests__/
    └── [feature]-flow.test.[ext] # Integration test

[e2e-folder]/
├── [feature].spec.[ext]          # E2E test
```

